high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk over to where the microwave is on the counter.
Pick up the spoon off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Put the spoon in the right sink basin and turn on the faucet, after a couple seconds turn the faucet off and remove the now clean spoon.
Turn left and walk over to the right side of the round black table.
Put the clean spoon on the round black table.
